              <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
              <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-gold sm:text-sm">100+ 5&#9733; Google Reviews</span>
          </div>

          <h1 class="font-display text-4xl leading-tight font-bold text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
            Get Summer-Ready.<br />
            <span class="italic text-gold">Ditch the Razor Forever.</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-white/70 lg:mx-0 lg:text-xl">
            6-session Brazilian + <strong class="text-white">FREE underarms</strong>. <span class="text-white">A $1,190+ value for just <strong>$800</strong>.</span>
          </p>
          <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-xl text-sm text-white/60 lg:mx-0">
            Led by <strong class="font-semibold text-white/80">Dr. Aditi Menon, MD</strong>, board-certified physician. Serving <strong class="font-semibold text-white/80">Millburn, NJ</strong> since 2019.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <a href="#claim-offer" data-lp-cta class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-full bg-gold px-5 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-black shadow-lg sm:px-8 sm:py-4 sm:text-lg">
              Claim $800 Summer Package &middot; Save $390
              <svg class="hidden h-5 w-5 sm:block" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 13.5L12 21m0 0l-7.5-7.5M12 21V3" /></svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-5 gap-y-1 text-xs text-white/50 lg:justify-start sm:text-sm">
            <span>New clients only</span>
            <span class="hidden sm:inline">&middot;</span>
            <span>6 sessions included</span>
            <span class="hidden sm:inline">&middot;</span>
            <span>Long-lasting smooth skin</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Board certified badge -->
          <div class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/10 px-3 py-1.5 backdrop-blur-sm sm:px-4 sm:py-2">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-white sm:text-sm">Board-Certified &middot; Medical-Grade Lasers</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== TRUST BAR (Purple) ========== -->
  <section class="bg-purple py-3.5">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-sm font-medium text-white sm:text-base">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
          Same-Week Appointments
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
          Medical-Grade Expertise
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
          State of the Art Equipment
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== PAIN POINTS ========== -->
  <section class="animate-on-scroll bg-cream py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-navy sm:text-4xl">
        Tired of the Endless<br class="hidden sm:inline" /> Shaving Cycle?
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-text-muted">
        You're not alone. These are the frustrations that bring patients to our door.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
        {[
          { title: "Razor burn and ingrown hairs", desc: "Red bumps, irritation, and painful ingrowns, no matter how careful you are with your razor." },
          { title: "Waxing that dreads every appointment", desc: "The pain, the regrowth, the awkward scheduling. And you have to let it grow out first." },
          { title: "Stubble that shows up the next day", desc: "You just shaved this morning and it's already coming back. It never ends." },
          { title: "Missing out on spontaneous plans", desc: "Beach invite? Pool party? You're always thinking about when you last shaved." },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-cream-dark bg-white p-6 text-left shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-navy">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-muted">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <p class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-text-muted">
        What if you could stop shaving, stop waxing, and feel <strong class="text-navy">confident in your skin all summer long?</strong> That's exactly what laser hair removal delivers, and right now, you can get started at an unbeatable price.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== THE OFFER ========== -->
  <section class="animate-on-scroll relative overflow-hidden bg-navy py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-navy-dark via-navy to-navy-light/80"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-gold/5 blur-3xl"></div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid items-center gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
          <picture>
            <source srcset="/images/laser-treatment-client.avif" type="image/avif" />
            <source srcset="/images/laser-treatment-client.webp" type="image/webp" />
            <img src="/images/laser-treatment-client.jpg" alt="Patient receiving professional laser hair removal at Menon MediSpa" class="h-auto w-full object-cover" width="1000" height="1000" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
          </picture>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gold">Summer Special</span>
          <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl">
            Brazilian + FREE Underarms.
            <span class="block italic text-gold">$1,190 Value. Just $800.</span>
          </h2>

          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-white">6-Session Brazilian Package &middot; $800</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-white/60">Full treatment series for lasting results</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-white">6-Session Underarms &middot; <span class="line-through text-white/40">$390</span> <span class="text-gold">FREE</span></div>
                <div class="text-sm text-white/60">Included at no extra charge with your Brazilian package</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-white">Complimentary Skin Health Analysis &middot; <span class="text-gold">FREE</span></div>
                <div class="text-sm text-white/60">A full assessment of your skin's texture, tone, and needs during your patch test visit</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-6 w-6 shrink-0 text-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.857-9.809a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.06 1.061l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-white">Significant Permanent Hair Reduction</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-white/60">Most patients see noticeable results after just 2-3 sessions</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-5 flex items-start gap-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gold/20 bg-gold/5 px-4 py-3">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2.166 4.999A11.954 11.954 0 0010 1.944 11.954 11.954 0 0017.834 5c.11.65.166 1.32.166 2.001 0 5.225-3.34 9.67-8 11.317C5.34 16.67 2 12.225 2 7c0-.682.057-1.35.166-2.001zm11.541 3.708a.75.75 0 00-1.214-.882l-3.483 4.79-1.88-1.88a.75.75 0 10-1.061 1.06l2.5 2.5a.75.75 0 001.137-.089l4-5.5z" clip-rule="evenodd" /></svg>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/80"><strong class="text-white">Just $50 down to hold your spot.</strong> The remaining $750 is only due after your patch test confirms you're a candidate. Not cleared? Your deposit is refunded.</p>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-white/40">New clients only · $50 deposit holds your spot · Balance ($750) due only after patch test clears you · Deposit refunded if you're not a candidate</p>

          <div class="mt-8">
            <a href="#claim-offer" data-lp-cta class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-gold px-7 py-3.5 text-base font-bold text-black shadow-lg">
              Claim This Deal &middot; Save $390
              <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 13.5L12 21m0 0l-7.5-7.5M12 21V3" /></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== HOW IT WORKS ========== -->
  <section class="animate-on-scroll bg-white py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-navy sm:text-4xl">
        How Laser Hair Removal Works
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-text-muted">
        Advanced laser technology targets hair at the root, destroying the follicle while leaving surrounding skin undamaged.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gold/10">
            <span class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-gold">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-display text-lg font-semibold text-navy">Patch Test + Skin Analysis</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-muted">We test your skin's response to the laser and perform a complimentary skin health analysis, assessing texture, tone, hydration, and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gold/10">
            <span class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-gold">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 font-display text-lg font-semibold text-navy">Treatment</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-muted">Quick, comfortable sessions every 4-6 weeks. Most areas take 15-30 minutes.</p>
